item.title: About Me
item.description: Work Experience Whirlpool June 2019 - October 2020 Develop Knowledge of OpenModelica and OMEdit to create simplified models in the pursuit of rapid simulation results. Create extensible models for use in future simulations. June 2018 - August 2018 Wrote Python scripts to automate the process of sorting, formatting, and filtering physical test data to be used for global refrigerator ice rate testing. Debugged and augmented existing Python scripts that extracted temperature and heat transfer simulation analysis data from ice making models.
